Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:05.83,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,950)\pos(409,478)\fsp5\blur2}砂的同盟国 木叶忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勘九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表蓮華
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到極限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喪家之犬 連叫都叫不出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:00:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死到臨頭還笑得出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這次是自己人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的同盟國
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂隱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去時當心點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後有情況我們還會來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時再見了 愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就愛嘴上佔便宜 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人就是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的人情 我會加倍奉還的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且待命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在情況緊急 怎麼能偷懶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 鹿丸有他自己的對策
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你要服從隊長的指示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃 看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孔雀 追兵的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我故意一路留下了足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒追上就頭疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 馬上就進入目標範圍內了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵有三個 其中一個就是我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他兩個人一對一地解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤立我愛羅後 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把他逼到逆鱗陣裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個人就交給我來解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實並不需要刻意把他逼到逆鱗陣裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過三個人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人就足夠應付了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孔雀飛翔雙劍.千猛風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操控風的忍者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不賴嘛 手鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有兩下子的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能破解我的千猛風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼 原來是個小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手鞠 你行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 同為風之忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人對付她就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧 我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大鐮鼬之術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風斬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這陣風是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手上的雙子劍能夠就著攻擊改變風向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並將力量增強到極致
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在後梅來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這兩把劍就不會耗費太多查克拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是查克拉有限的你能堅持到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在是人質了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吸引他的誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍眼伸縮劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎 這就是龍眼伸縮劍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過中心的鐵線 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將短劍串聯起來的伸縮劍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像竹蛇一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人懷念 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候經常用來練習傀儡術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果技術熟練 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來就會像真的蛇一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過既然看穿了 就沒什麼可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然都是機關忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但與我相比 你的不過是玩具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有辦法應付嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不至於依賴你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會立刻追上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來吧 我們玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必逞強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小看我會沒命的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒命的是你才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手吧 大花臉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 這不是單純的伸縮劍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會感應我的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後變成龍形增強力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅 不好意思 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得多花一點時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水虎 你在這裡等那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後引他去逆鱗陣 知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你再前進一步的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅 跟我交手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸 我們要等到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急 埋伏需要做很多準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在志乃 寧次跟雛田 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在替我們處理這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 一共有三處戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是寄壞蟲的雌性氣味袋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了它 無論你身處何處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子都會找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們先出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 看你們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣 已經開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 牙和丁次去森林的西側
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟井野去東北的山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人跟小李
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們負責森林的西北側
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人一組 相互支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報恩作戰 正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻我等了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡者採用了一對一的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼戰場不在一條直線上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是結界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是謹慎一點好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下你就無處藏身了 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能避開我所有的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 只好用那招了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風遁.龍卷颶風
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 完全沒變化嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐 看來風不喜歡你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負這才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風反轉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 放開我 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒招了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為能多玩一會兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才像話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次會是什麼玩具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑 這種破銅爛鐵還想打敗我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的劍才是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 變成三條龍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你的優點只是跑得比較快而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來烏鴉不和黑螞蟻聯手就發揮不出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是砂瀑我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的砂子裡有多少查克拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代價就是要你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂縛柩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個砂浴不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然把砂裡的查克拉給…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這副鎧甲能吸乾查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想休息了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就永遠躺著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是千鈞一髮 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子模仿術成功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂的同盟國
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在前面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家全力以赴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前盆地裡並未發現異常的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有結界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我 我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會還你一個人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手一開始的目的就是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他們居然會利用地形
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅的形式就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們現在也無法抽身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:22:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了 鳴人 小李
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:22:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有你們能救我愛羅了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封鎖的砂 水虎的反擊
